column5: I had several VERY GOOD sites bookmarked from you guys but my computer crashed Super Bowl Sunday....I guess it couldn't take the stress...  ...but anyways, can you guys PLEASE list some of the sites where I can rent a private cottage or even a GOOD commercial cottage in the near future.......THANKS for your time...  Bob

Cottage Directories http://www.northerncomfort.com/cottages.htm http://www.clrm.ca/ http://www.cottagelink.com/rentals.shtml http://www.cottagesincanada.com/index2.asp?lang=e http://www.cottagesontheweb.com/ http://www.cottageportal.com/ListOntario.cfm http://www.haliburtoncottages.com/

Thanks bassman....was away for a couple of days at the largest Sportsmen Show in the NE....Harrisburg, PA....great time with the wife....  But anyways I should of mentioned I am interested in the Kawarthan Lakes but I just have to sort through some of the links you listed......boy did I have a few nice cottages saved in my book marks before this computer crashed.......thanks again.  Bob
